I loved these when I was a bit to young to get them on VHS but the memories of them were good. The films themselves don't hold up as good as my nostalgia would like them to but I have enjoyed the repeat viewings of them. If you haven't seen them and you like 80's, awkward situations and pretty girls in bikinis then you might enjoy this for the night.
